# Admin Dashboard

## Overview
You are building a secure, enterprise-grade Admin Dashboard (Gbox360 context) that enables platform admins and enterprise account admins to manage tenants, configurations, ingestion status, and system health. This dashboard includes a dedicated audit, monitoring, and replay controls layer, an immutable Admin Audit Logs page, and a User Management page that spans across tenant accounts. The solution must emphasize reliability, auditability, and strict access control, with a focus on end-to-end admin workflows, robust data handling, and a premium fintech aesthetic aligned to the provided design system.

Key goals:
- Provide a centralized admin hub for core governance tasks: tenants/configs, ingestion health, system health overview, and incident alerts.
- Empower admins with auditable visibility into ingestion health, user actions, exports, weight simulations, and replay operations, including raw payload references.
- Offer immutable audit logs with queryability, pagination, and raw payload drill-downs.
- Enable cross-tenant user management: users, roles, invitations, and deactivations with tenant-scoped scopes and bulk actions.
- Enforce strict role-based access control (RBAC): only platform admins and enterprise admins can access admin sections.

